public class MechanicalEdge
extends graph.components.NamedWeightedEdge<ReferenceFrame>

This class implements a graph theoretical edge associated to a mechanical component's properties for a given domain (translational or rotational).

MechanicalEdge

public MechanicalEdge(java.lang.String name,
                      ReferenceFrame source,
                      ReferenceFrame target,
                      ComponentType type,

Creates a graph theoretical edge that represents a components properties in a certain domain (translational or rotational).

Parameters:
name - is the name of the component being represented
source - is the source reference frame of the component being represented
target - is the source reference frame of the component being represented
type - is the type of component being represented
domain - is the domain in which this edge represents the component's properties
